F. W. SCHUTZ v. SOUTHERN PACIFIC COMPANY et al. No. 8222. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 8, 1936. Huston, Huston & Huston, of Woodland, Cal., for appellant. Devlin & Devlin & Diepenbrock, of Sacramento, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
